    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Phrases for Suggesting a Gift"
        },
        "text": "When you want to suggest a gift, you can start with 'ربما...' (rubbamā...) meaning 'perhaps...' or 'قد يكون...' (qad yakūn...) meaning 'it might be...'. You can also use 'ماذا عن...؟' (mādhā 'an...?) meaning 'What about...?'",
